Questions:
Which of the following procedures is considered experimental in the BMT CTN 1902 study?
A) Standard maintenance therapy with lenalidomide;
B) Use of chemotherapy drugs fludarabine and cyclophosphamide;
C) Collection of blood cells through leukapheresis for standard diagnostic purposes;
D) Administration of bb2121 CAR T-cell therapy following autologous hematopoietic cell transplantation.

Correct answer: D
